npm i express body-parser mongoose concurrently
npm i -D nodemon
parm -D to dev dependencies
concurrently - to run more than one npm script, like to run front and back-end at the same time

create-react-app
npm i bootstrap reactstrap uuid react-transition-group

uuid -> generate random ids to insert into database

Installing Redux
npm i redux react-redux redux-thunk 

Installing Axios to http requests
npm install axios

Set UP Heroku
Install Heroku CLI.exe on the website

heroku login
heroku create
git push heroku master
